                dk.frv.enav.ins.ais.VesselStaticData staticData,
                double sog,
                double cogR,

        Updates all the vessel layers with position, data and heading where needed. Shows them on the map depending on mapScale.
        Parameters:
        trueHeading - Direction of vessel icon
        lat - Latitude position of vessel
        lon - Longitude position of vessel
        staticData - Static information of vessel
        sog - Speed over ground
        cogR - Course over ground in radians
        mapScale - Scale of the chartMap
